106
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,100
On passe aux aspects pharmacocinétiques.

107
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:01,760
Chez la femme enceinte, il y a tendance

108
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:05,160
